f\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c4f2564274906b35a19825e8fc769210874a07ea","tid":428870,"uid":29080,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-09T00:47:29.000Z","msg":"含咩話?"},{"pid":"405a9a88d829d8e0a68b9e19243342b6df7a3cbc","tid":428870,"uid":121439,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-09T00:49:25.000Z","msg":"含乜撚野識佢老鼠咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a9af75505f7239149be79590a5c3ae109cd12daf","tid":428870,"uid":135206,"like":6,"dislike":6,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-09T00:49:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>唔撚識呀</blockquote><br />\n仲咁撚大聲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n人地而家支那最紅嗰幾件 的確係年年搵緊幾億 你唔識人唔通等佢黎識你條死毒撚？ <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 你老母咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c428dd129a29b6222ac6a0e4f35fb5a33d5d1528","tid":428870,"uid":60982,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-09T00:52:53.000Z","msg":"幾年後睇返想當年為錢走真係明智 依家鹿含一年搵既可能係EXO10年都搵唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"409cb4c62c41c906ca45c5652856ce7925ceef0f","tid":428870,"uid":55846,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-09T01:20:38.000Z","msg":"男定女"},{"pid":"99b436fee3afa5f5d8075af4ed30c5d804ca45e2","tid":428870,"uid":16528,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-09T01:34:26.000Z","msg":"邊撚個"},{"pid":"b53b10dd09fa0f9957566da28697e803a313fb16","tid":428870,"uid":123224,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-09T01:54:35.000Z","msg":"男人老狗打扮到女人咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0d2862659391263c0fc4f5d9c081001f4af35cb6","tid":428870,"uid":125079,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"repl